{"tid":564030,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[J2] 年初二10:05pm 戀上春樹 (染谷將太 ,長澤正美)","createTime":"2018-02-17T13:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T17:06:31.000Z","uid":35166,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"dcea0e6ee902f34ad65afebc9381c5aeab1df0bc","tid":564030,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.misugi.com/tw/images/wjcast.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.misugi.com%2Ftw%2Fimages%2Fwjcast.jpg&h=adb75603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-E0Wbq2l2QjY/VjqxhnVxBcI/AAAAAAAAAJM/XsbuYQuYDjk/s1600/Free%2Bdownload%2Bbluray%2B1080p%2B720p%2Bmovie%2Bgoogle%2Bdrive%2BWood%2BJob%252C%2BJapan%252C%2B2014%252C%2BShinobu%2BYaguchi%252C%2BMasami%2BNagasawa%252C%2BSh%25C3%25B4ta%2BSometani%252C%2BHideaki%2BIt%25C3%25B4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-E0Wbq2l2QjY%2FVjqxhnVxBcI%2FAAAAAAAAAJM%2FXsbuYQuYDjk%2Fs1600%2FFree%252Bdownload%252Bbluray%252B1080p%252B720p%252Bmovie%252Bgoogle%252Bdrive%252BWood%252BJob%25252C%252BJapan%25252C%252B2014%25252C%252BShinobu%252BYaguchi%25252C%252BMasami%252BNagasawa%25252C%252BSh%2525C3%2525B4ta%252BSometani%25252C%252BHideaki%252BIt%2525C3%2525B4.jpg&h=d731d59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n高中生平野勇氣（染谷將太 飾）自小生活無憂無慮，直至放榜肥佬，考不上大學，女友鄙視提出分手，才驚覺自己前景一片暗淡。就在這時候，他偶然看到「林業見習班」招生，傳單上的宣傳大使更竟然是女神級（長澤正美 飾）！勇氣決定離開大城市，走入深山學斬樹，但入山後，才發現山裡沒有便利店，也沒有手機訊號，有的只是野鹿大蛇怪蟲、野獸般的教官（伊藤英明 飾）、樹和很高的樹！食慣嘆慣的勇氣很快便氣餒，密謀偷走，豈料幻想已久的女神突然出現，激發他捱下去的鬥心。漸漸地，勇氣在一無所有的山上，愛上了古靈精怪的村民，發現人與大自然的連繫，還找到傳統林業的真正意義。"},{"pid":"2fe891fbf9fb497046a2c27cf8bfa42755ccaa51","tid":564030,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"好似有配音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3604b1750798c2fb508d9dd9a4c82515e706c4d9","tid":564030,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"reply